description	"Captain Bostuco

^2Weaponry:
- Dual Heavy Blaster Pistols (4)

^6Inventory:
- Electrobinoculars

^8Attributes:
- Healing (2)
- Rally

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS1]
- Dash (2) ^3[CS2]

Bostuco was a Human male who served in the Onderonian military, having earned the rank of Captain. He was the leader of the security detail that guarded the Sky Ramp, one of the passageways that led to the Iziz Royal Palace on his native world of Onderon."